			<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="text">
				<p>As mobility problems have become the norm for many seniors and people who have disabilities, climbing stairs can pose a significant challenge. Inability to walk can limit autonomy and increase the likelihood of falling, which makes stairs a crucial issue to take care of. Recent data indicates that falling from and on steps and stairs &#8230; <a title="Innovative Ways to Get Past Stair Barriers" class="read-more" href="https://newsodin.com/innovative-ways-to-get-past-stair-barriers/" aria-label="Read more about Innovative Ways to Get Past Stair Barriers">Read more</a></p>
