			<span class="posted-on"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2025-07-21T06:40:04+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">July 21, 2025</time></span> <span class="byline">by <span class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemtype="https://schema.org/Person" itemscope><a class="url fn n" href="https://newsodin.com/author/newseditor/" title="View all posts by newseditor" rel="author" itemprop="url"><span class="author-name" itemprop="name">newseditor</span></a></span></span> 		</div>
