							<img width="1600" height="1068" src="https://newsodin.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Whisky.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Whisky" itemprop="image" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://newsodin.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Whisky.jpg 1600w, https://newsodin.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Whisky-300x200.jpg 300w, https://newsodin.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Whisky-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https://newsodin.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Whisky-768x513.jpg 768w, https://newsodin.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Whisky-1536x1025.jpg 1536w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" />
